1    Taagken qilagami aliightuq sangwaa saghiighanapiglleghhii liisimakusighqaghput piyaghqamun. Taawa maaghraghvinlek yaqulget, tagitilghiit maaghraghvinlegneng seghleliilleghllagneng. Taakut seghleliilleghllaget taaqniitkeftii Kiyaghneghem sakraalleghllagan.
2    Taagken esghaghaqa kelliisugnilnguq meghraakegtaq siqinwaaghestun, akumngalghii keneghmeng. Esghaghankallu kayaalqiikat teghikusalluugmeng, nangaghneghaneng, aatghanllu number-nganeng. Nekevghatnguftut saaghwaghni kelliim, harp-elightuulluteng Kiyaghneghem tuunegkiitneng ellngitnun.
3    Ilagaghaqeftut ilagaatanganeng Moses-em, (Kiyaghneghem qepghaghtenga), ilagaatanganengllu Penniighaghaam: “Kaay, Ataneq Kiyaghneq Aghtughyaghqaghhaanghiteghllak, qepghalleghten seghleghllaguut, allaaghlluwhaghllaguut! Kaay, umiilgat nunam yugita, elpek salleghten elqughutngaatlu ipanguutlu!
4    Ataneq, qamagtengngwaaghluteng yuget alikelleqaaten, quulvaghlleqaatlu aatghen! Ellnginaaguten agleghnalghii! Qamagtengngwaaghluteng nunatat manigughyaghtughlleqaaten, qayughllak liisimakegkangat nanqigtilleghten elqughutngalghiit!”
5    Taam kingunganeng esghaghaqa qilagmi qelpeghtekangat Temple-a. (Agleghnalleghpigaaguq Na, ellngan yugita liisimakusiqaat Kiyaghneq tawanniluku.)
6    Taagken maaghraghvinlek yaqulget aanleghaatut Temple-meng kelqelluteng maaghraghvinlegneng seghleliilleghllagneng. Tamaghhaghmeng atkuyaaghulluteng qateghrakegtameng nighulghiimeng, sakimagmegteggun gold-meng tafsiluteng.
7    Taagken ataasim unguvalghiim estamaneng taakuneng, gold-meng sagneliqughii maaghraghvinlek yaqulget. Taakut sagneghet imighngaat sakraalleghllaaganeng Kiyaghneghem, kiyaghlleghhii quunperugllak kenlengunaan.
8    Temple-em ilunga agepsughqaagaa Kiyaghneghem nighughqellghanengllu, aghtughyaghqaanghillghanengllu. Kina alngunak iteghnaanghituq Temple-mun kenlanga maaghraghvinlek seghleliilleghllaget kenletghuutellghitnun, tagitkiit maaghraghvinlek yaqulget.
 
